      bio: "Mark keeps Highfield running like clockwork. With a background in building and project management, nothing is too big or too small for him to tackle. Residents love how quickly he responds to every request.",
      funfact: "Mark once rebuilt a classic 1967 Ford Mustang from scratch in his garage — it took him 3 years but he still drives it on weekends."
